0tariffs%20will%20apply%20to%20%26quot%3Beveryday%20items%26quot%3B%20such%20as%20American%20beer%2C%20wine%20and%20bourbon%20as%20well%20as%20fruits%2C%20vegetables%2C%20consumer%20appliances%2C%20lumber%20and%20plastics%2C%20he%20added%20--%20%26quot%3Bwith%20much%2C%20much%20more.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BWe're%20certainly%20not%20looking%20to%20escalate.%20But%20we%20will%20stand%20up%20for%20Canada%2C%20for%20Canadians%2C%20for%20Canadian%20jobs%2C%26quot%3B%20Trudeau%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrudeau%20said%20Canada%20has%20been%20at%20the%20US's%20side%20in%20its%20%26quot%3Bdarkest%20hours%26quot%3B%20from%20the%20Iran%20hostage%20crisis%20and%20war%20in%20Afghanistan%2C%20to%20deadly%20natural%20disasters%20such%20as%20Hurricane%20Katrina%20and%20the%20recent%20California%20wildfires.%20%26quot%3BIf%20President%20Trump%20wants%20to%20usher%20in%20a%20new%20golden%20age%20for%20the%20United%20States%2C%20the%20better%20path%20is%20to%20partner%20with%20Canada%2C%20not%20to%20punish%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina%20too%20vowed%20%26quot%3Bcorresponding%20countermeasures%26quot%3B%20against%20the%20new%20tariffs%20and%20file%20a%20claim%20against%20Washington%20at%20the%20World%20Trade%20Organization.%20%26quot%3BThere%20are%20no%20winners%20in%20a%20trade%20war%20or%20tariff%20war%2C%26quot%3B%20China's%20foreign%20ministry%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20additional%20duties%20would%20%26quot%3Binevitably%20affect%20and%20damage%20future%20bilateral%20cooperation%20on%20drug%20control%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeijing%20urged%20%26quot%3Bthe%20US%20to%20correct%20its%20erroneous%20practices%2C%20meet%20China%20halfway%2C%20face%20up%20to%20its%20problems%2C%20have%20frank%20dialogues%2C%20strengthen%20cooperation%20and%20manage%20differences%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20equality%2C%20mutual%20benefit%20and%20mutual%20respect%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESheinbaum%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20said%20she%20had%20told%20her%20economy%20mini