old%20BI.%20He%20said%20it%20would%20likely%20increase%20pressure%20on%20the%20governments%20of%20Mexico%2C%20Canada%2C%20and%20China%20to%20negotiate%20quickly%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ewith%20the%20Trump%20administration%20to%20meet%20its%20policy%20demands%20over%20border%20security%20%E2%80%94%20but%20the%20move%20is%20risky.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECanadian%20Prime%20Minister%20Justin%20Trudeau%20on%20Saturday%20evening%20announced%2025%25%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrudeau-canada-retaliatory-tariffs-against-us-donald-trump-trade-war-2025-2%3Fmrfhud%3Dtrue%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eretaliatory%20tariffs%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20goods%20imported%20from%20the%20US%2C%20in%20response%20to%20the%20tariffs%20Trump%20levied%20on%20Canadian%20imports.%20Mexican%20President%20Claudia%20Sheinbaum%20late%20Saturday%20also%20imposed%20retaliatory%2025%25%20tariffs%20on%20imported%20US%20goods%20in%20response%20to%20Trump's%20trade%20moves%2C%20per%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Famericas%2Fmexican-president-orders-retaliatory-tariffs-against-us-2025-02-02%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EReuters%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBI%20previously%20reported%20economists%20predict%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-china-trump-trade-war-tariffs-retaliation-counter-measures-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChina%3C%2Fa%3E%20will%20respond%20similarly%2C%20with%20retaliatory%20tariffs%2C%20limiting%20exports%20of%20raw%20materials%20used%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frare-earths-tech-war-explainer-chips-ai-china-us-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esemiconductor%20production%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20or%20other%20changes%20to%20its%20trade%20policies%20to%20squeeze%20the%20US%20economy.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ENo%20such%20measures%20have%20yet%20been%20announced.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20consumers%20need%20to%20prepare%20that%20this%20is%20going%20to%20affect%20everybody%20in%20the%20country%2C%20not%20just%20a%20couple%20of%20businesses%2C%26quot%3B%20Guerra%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fretailers-small-businesses-react-trump-trade-tariffs-2025-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738470589000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F679eb354bfebcc4d029d76e6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fretailers-small-businesses-react-trump-trade-tariffs-2025-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Donald%20Trump%20on%20Saturday%20traded%20new%20tariffs%20on%20imports%20with%20Canada%20and%20Mexico.%20Consumers%20and%20retailers%20are%20preparing%20for%20price%20hikes%20in%20response.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ktangalakislippert%40businessinsider.com%20(Katherine%20Tangalakis-Lippert)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A40%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fretailers-small-businesses-react-trump-trade-tariffs-2025-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BMade%20To%20Lick%20Toilet%20Seat%26quot%3B%3A%20Teen%20Dies%20By%20Suicide%2C%20Mother%20Alleges%20Ragging%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWeeks%20after%20a%2015-year-old%20schoolboy%20in%20Kerala's%20Kochi%20died%20by%20suicide%2C%20his%20mother%20has%20alleged%20that%20brutal%20ragging%20crushed%20her%20son%20and%20pushed%20him%20toward%20death.%20In%20a%20statement%20posted%20on%20Instagram%2C%20Rajna%20PM%20alleged%20that%20her%20son%2C%20Mihir%20Ahammed%2C%20was%20beaten%20up%2C%20verbally%20abused%20and%20forced%20to%20lick%20the%20toilet%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20have%20registered%20a%20case%20of%20suicide%2C%20but%20Mihir's%20mother%20has%20said%20she%20had%20written%20to%20Chief%20Minister%20Pinarayi%20Vijayan's%20office%20and%20the%20Kerala%20police%20chief%20and%20sought%20an%20immediate%20and%20impartial%20probe%20into%20her%20son's%20death.%20Mihir%20died%20by%20suicide%20on%20January%2015%20after%20he%20jumped%20from%20their%2026th-floor%20flat%20in%20Kochi's%20Thripunithara%2C%20barely%20an%20hour%20after%20he%20returned%20from%20school.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETeen's%20Mother%20Seeks%20Justice%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20his%20death%2C%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20began%20gathering%20information%20to%20understand%20why%20Mihir%20took%20such%20a%20drastic%20step.%20Through%20conversations%20with%20his%20friends%2C%20schoolmates%2C%20and%20by%20reviewing%20social%20media%20messages%2C%20we%20uncovered%20the%20horrific%20reality%20of%20what%20he%20endured.%20Mihir%20was%20subjected%20to%20brutal%20ragging%2C%20bullying%2C%20and%20physical%20assault%20by%20a%20gang%20of%20students%20at%20school%20and%20on%20the%20school%20bus%2C%26quot%3B%20his%20mother%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20evidence%20we%20gathered%20paints%20a%20chilling%20picture.%20Mihir%20was%20beaten%2C%20verbally%20abused%2C%20and%20forced%20to%20endure%20unimaginable%20humiliation%20even%20on%20his%20last%20day.%20He%20was%20forcibly%20taken%20to%20the%20washroom%2C%20made%20to%20lick%20a%20toilet%20seat%2C%20and%20had%20his%20head%20pushed%20into%20the%20toilet%20while%20it%20was%20flushed.%20These%20acts%20of%20cruelty%20broke%20him%20in%20ways%20we%20cannot%20fathom.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMihir's%20mother%20said%20he%20was%20bullied%20for%20his%20skin%20colour.%20%26quot%3BThey%20didn't%20end%20the%20cruelty%20even%20after%20his%20death.%20A%20shocking%20chat%20screenshot%20reveals%20the%20extent%20of%20their%20cruelty.%20They%20messaged%20'fxxk%20ni*ga%20he%20actually%20died'%20and%20celebrated%20his%20death%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBig%20Charge%20Against%20School%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERajna%20PM%20said%20Mihir's%20friends%20had%20started%20an%20Instagram%20page%20titled%20'Justice%20for%20Mihir'%20to%20amplify%20their%20demand%20for%20justice.%20%26quot%3BHowever%2C%20the%20page%20has%20now%20been%20deleted%2C%20and%20there%20are%20reports%20that%20the%20school%20is%20intimidating%20students%20to%20suppress%20the%20truth.%20When%20I%20approached%20the%20school%20authorities%20with%20evidence%20and%20demanded%20accountability%2C%20they%20only%20informed%20me%20that%20the%20information%20was%20forwarded%20to%20the%20police.%20I%20strongly%20believe%20they%20are%20attempting%20to%20cover%20up%20these%20incidents%20to%20protect%20the%20school's%20reputation%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%C2%A0The%20teen's%20mother%20said%20she%20has%20approached%20the%20Chief%20Minister's%20office%20and%20DGP%20for%20immediate%20action.%20%26quot%3BI%20fear%20delays%20in%20gathering%20digital%20evidence%20may%20allow%20the%20culprits%20to%20erase%20their%20tracks.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Rajna%20said%20she%20had%20also%20flagged%20the%20incident%20to%20the%20Kerala%20State%20Commission%20for%20Protection%20of%20Child%20Rights.%20According%20to%20a%20Mathrubhumi%20report%2C%20the%20child%20rights%20body's%20chairman%20has%20confirmed%20that%20the%20panel%20has%20taken%20note%20of%20the%20teen's%20tragic%20death.%20She%20has%20also%20alleged%20that%20the%20school's%20vice-principal%20harassed%20Mihir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKerala%20Education%20V%20Sivankutty%20has%20ordered%20a%20thorough%20investigation%20into%20the%20chilling%20incident%2C%20Mathrubhumi%20has%20reported.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECelebrities%20Speak%20Out%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETop%20actors%20have%20spoken%20out%20against%20the%20ragging%20culture%20and%20mourned%20the%20loss%20of%20a%20young%20life.%20Samantha%20Ruth%20Prabhu%20said%20the%20news%20had%20%26quot%3Babsolutely%20shattered%26quot%3B%20her.%20%26quot%3BIt's%202025.%20Yet%2C%20we've%20lost%20another%20bright%20young%20life%2C%20snuffed%20out%20because%20a%20few%20individuals%2C%20filled%20with%20hate%20and%20venom%20pushed%20someone%20to%20the%20brink!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20Mihir's%20death%20is%20a%20'reminder%20that%20bullying%2C%20harassment%2C%20and%20ragging%20are%20not%20just%20'harmless%20traditions'%20or%20'rites%20of%20passage'.%20%26quot%3BThey%20are%20violence%20-%20psychological%2C%20emotional%2C%20and%20sometimes%2C%20even%20physical.%20We%20have%20stringent%20anti-ragging%20laws%20apparently%2C%20yet%20our%20students%20continue%20to%20suffer%20in%20silence%2C%20afraid%20to%20speak%20up%2C%20afraid%20of%20consequences%2C%20afraid%20that%20no%20one%20will%20listen.%20Where%20are%20we%20failing%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EActor%20Prithiviraj%20Sukumaran%20said%20in%20an%20Instagram%20post%2C%20%26quot%3BParents%2C%20homes%2C%20teachers%2C%20schools%2C%20Empathy%20is%20lesson%20no.%201%26quot%3B.%20Actor%20Keerthy%20Suresh%20described%20the%20teen's%20death%20as%20%26quot%3Bheart-wrenching%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BIf%20ragging%20starts%20in%20school%20and%20a%20group%20of%20kids%20has%20tortured%20a%20boy%20to%20the%20extent%20that%20he%20took%20his%20own%20life%2C%20what%20a%20shame!%20Can't%20stop%20thinking%20of%20this%20grieving%20mother%20and%20her%20family.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738470240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2F9flieho8_kerala-teen_625x300_02_February_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkochi-ragging-suicide-mihir-ahammed-made-to-lick-toilet-seat-teen-dies-by-suicide-mother-alleges-ragging-7614832%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Weeks%20after%20a%2015-year-old%20schoolboy%20in%20Kerala's%20Kochi%20died%20by%20suicide%2C%20his%20mother%20has%20alleged%20that%20brutal%20ragging%20crushed%20her%20son%20and%20pushed%20him%20toward%20death%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkochi-ragging-suicide-mihir-ahammed-made-to-lick-toilet-seat-teen-dies-by-suicide-mother-alleges-ragging-7614832%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BIsn't%20He%20Human%3F%26quot%3B%3A%20Plight%20Of%20Hardik%2C%20Stripped%20Of%20T20I%20Captaincy%2C%20Highlighed%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EHardik%20Pandya%20was%20at%20his%20best%20with%20the%20bat%20during%20India's%20fourth%20T20I%20of%20the%20five-match%20series%20against%20England%20in%20Pune%20on%20Saturday.%20The%20all-rounder%20played%20a%2053-run%20knock%20off%2030%20balls%20with%20the%20help%20of%204%20fours%20and%20as%20many%20sixes.%20It%20was%20a%20slow%20start%20for%20Hardik%20in%20the%20innings%20as%20India%20were%20struggling%20at%2079%20for%205%20at%20one%20stage.%20However%2C%20he%20accelerated%20brilliantly%20to%20propel%20India%20to%20a%20big%20total.%20The%20side%20eventually%20won%20the%20game%20by%2015%20runs%20that%20also%20helped%20them%20clinch%20the%20series.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20India%20player%20Mohammad%20Kaif%20heaped%20huge%20praise%20on%20Hardik%20Pandya%20after%20his%20performance.%20Kaif%20also%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20all-rounder%20faced%20a%20lot%20of%20backlash%20last%20year%2C%20yet%20continues%20to%20deliver%20for%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHardik%20had%20to%20go%20through%20a%20lot%20after%20he%20replaced%20Rohit%20Sharma%20as%20Mumbai%20Indians%20captain%20ahead%20of%20IPL%202024.%20While%20the%20move%20faced%20a%20lot%20of%20criticism%2C%20Hardik%20was%20subjected%20to%20crowd%20boos%20even%20at%20MI's%20home%20ground%20Wankhede%20Stadium.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOvercoming%20the%20harsh%20treatment%2C%20Hardik%20played%20an%20intrumental%20role%20in%20India's%20T20%20World%20Cup%20title%20victory%20later%20that%20year.%20He%20was%20the%20designated%20vice-captain%20of%20the%20squad%20till%20the%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20tournament%2C%20India's%20then%20T20I%20captain%20Rohit%20Sharma%20called%20time%20on%20his%20international%20career%20and%20it%20seemed%20t