0on%20'Viksit%20Delhi-Viksit%20Bharat%2C'%20Jaishankar%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWhenever%20I%20visit%20foreign%20countries%2C%20I%20hide%20one%20thing%20from%20the%20world.%20I%20feel%20ashamed%20to%20go%20abroad%20and%20say%20that%20people%20living%20in%20the%20national%20capital%20do%20not%20get%20houses%2C%20do%20not%20get%20gas%20cylinders%2C%20or%20piped%20water%20under%20Jal%20Jeevan%20Mission%20and%20do%20not%20get%20the%20benefit%20of%20Ayushman%20Bharat.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20unfortunate%20that%20in%20the%20last%2010%20years%2C%20Delhi%20has%20been%20left%20behind.%20The%20residents%20of%20Delhi%20are%20not%20given%20their%20rights%20to%20water%2C%20electricity%2C%20gas%2C%20cylinders%2C%20health%20treatment.%20If%20the%20government%20here%20does%20not%20give%20you%20your%20rights%20then%20on%205th%20February%20you%20also%20think%20that%20this%20government%20should%20be%20changed.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20praised%20PM%20Narendra%20Modi's%20leadership%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BEver%20since%20Narendra%20Modi%20became%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20the%20thinking%20of%20the%20world%20about%20India%20has%20changed%20a%20lot.%20The%20world%20sees%20that%20when%20the%20economic%20situation%20in%20the%20whole%20world%20is%20down%2C%20we%20are%20still%20maintaining%20six%20to%20seven%20per%20cent%20growth%20rate.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2070%20assembly%20seats%20in%20Delhi%20will%20go%20to%20polls%20on%20February%205%2C%20with%20the%20counting%20of%20votes%20scheduled%20for%20February%208.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20MP%20Sanjay%20Singh%20exuded%20confidence%20in%20his%20party%20winning%20more%20than%2060%20seats%20in%20the%2070-seat%20legislature%20in%20the%20upcoming%20Delhi%20assembly%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20media%20persons%2C%20Sanjay%20Singh%20said%20that%20the%20Arvind%20Kejriwal-led%20government%20will%20be%20formed%20in%20Delhi%20with%20a