uot%3BThe%20shells%20hit%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20vegetable%20market%2C%20that's%20why%20the%20victims%20and%20the%20wounded%20are%20so%20many%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20survivor%20told%20AFP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20RSF%20denied%20carrying%20out%20the%20attack%2C%20which%20French%20medical%20charity%20Doctors%20Without%20Borders%20(MSF)%20said%20caused%20%26quot%3Butter%20carnage%26quot%3B%20at%20the%20hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAcross%20the%20Nile%20in%20Khartoum%20proper%2C%20two%20civilians%20were%20killed%20and%20dozens%20wounded%20in%20an%20air%20strike%20on%20an%20RSF-controlled%20area%2C%20said%20the%20local%20Emergency%20Response%20Room%2C%20one%20of%20hundreds%20of%20volunteer%20groups%20coordinating%20emergency%20care%20across%20Sudan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20RSF%20has%20used%20drones%20in%20attacks%2C%20including%20on%20Saturday%2C%20the%20fighter%20jets%20of%20the%20regular%20armed%20forces%20maintain%20a%20monopoly%20on%20air%20strikes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20the%20RSF%20and%20the%20army%20have%20been%20repeatedly%20accused%20of%20targeting%20civilians%20and%20indiscriminately%20shelling%20residential%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20killing%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20people%2C%20the%20war%20has%20uprooted%20more%20than%2012%20million%20and%20decimated%20Sudan's%20fragile%20infrastructure%2C%20forcing%20most%20health%20facilities%20out%20of%20service.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMetres%20From%20Hospital%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMSF's%20general%20secretary%20Chris%20Lockyear%20was%20at%20the%20Al-Nao%20Hospital%20Saturday%2C%20where%20he%20said%20%26quot%3Bthe%20morgue%20is%20full%20of%20dead%20bodies%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20can%20see%20the%20lives%20of%20men%2C%20women%20and%20children%20torn%20apart%2C%20with%20injured%20people%20lying%20in%20every%20possible%20space%20in%20the%20emergency%20room%20as%20medics%20do%20what%20they%20can%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20volunteer%20at%20the%20hospital%20told%20AFP%20it%20faced%20dire%20shortages%20of%20%26quot%3Bshrouds%2C%20blood%20donors%20and%20stretchers%20to%20transport%20the%20wounded%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAl-Nao%2C%20one%20of%20the%20last%20medical%20facilities%20operating%20in%20Omdurman%2C%20has%20been%20repeatedly%20attacked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Sudanese%20doctors'%20union%2C%20one%20shell%20fell%20%26quot%3Bjust%20metres%20away%26quot%3B%20from%20the%20hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20union%20said%20most%20of%20the%20victims%20were%20women%20and%20children%2C%20and%20called%20on%20nurses%20and%20doctors%20in%20the%20area%20to%20head%20to%20the%20hospital%20to%20relieve%20a%20%26quot%3Bsevere%20shortage%20of%20medical%20staff%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fighting%20in%20the%20capital%20comes%20weeks%20after%20the%20army%20launched%20an%20offensive%20across%20central%20Sudan%2C%20reclaiming%20Al-Jazira%20state%20capital%20Wad%20Madani%20before%20setting%20its%20sights%20on%20Khartoum.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20RSF%20has%20since%20remained%20in%20control%20of%20the%20road%20between%20Wad%20Madani%20and%20Khartoum%2C%20but%20on%20Saturday%20an%20army-allied%20militia%20claimed%20control%20of%20the%20towns%20of%20Tamboul%2C%20Rufaa%2C%20Al-Hasaheisa%20and%20Al-Hilaliya%2C%20some%20125%20kilometres%20(77%20miles)%20southeast%20of%20the%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20group%2C%20the%20Sudan%20Shield%20Forces%2C%20is%20led%20by%20Abu%20Aqla%20Kaykal%2C%20who%20defected%20from%20the%20RSF%20last%20year%20and%20has%20been%20accused%20of%20atrocities%20against%20civilians%20both%20during%20his%20tenure%20with%20the%20RSF%20and%20now%20on%20the%20army's%20side.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESudan%20remains%20effectively%20split%2C%20with%20the%20RSF%20in%20control%20of%20nearly%20all%20of%20the%20vast%20western%20region%20of%20Darfur%20and%20swathes%20of%20the%20south%2C%20and%20the%20army%20controlling%20the%20country's%20east%20and%20north.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECounter-Offensive%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20months%20of%20stalemate%20in%20greater%20Khartoum%2C%20the%20army%20has%20broken%20RSF%20sieges%20on%20several%20bases%20in%20the%20capital%2C%20including%20its%20headquarters%2C%20pushing%20the%20paramilitary%20increasingly%20into%20the%20city's%20outskirts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWitnesses%20said%20Saturday's%20bombardment%20of%20Omdurman%20came%20from%20the%20city's%20western%20outskirts%2C%20where%20the%20RSF%20remains%20in%20control.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20came%20a%20day%20after%20RSF%20commander%20Mohamed%20Hamdan%20Daglo%20vowed%20to%20retake%20the%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20expelled%20them%20(from%20Khartoum)%20before%2C%20and%20we%20will%20expel%20them%20again%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20troops%20in%20a%20rare%20video%20address.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGreater%20Khartoum%20has%20been%20a%20key%20battleground%20in%20nearly%2022%20months%20of%20fighting%20between%20the%20army%20and%20the%20RSF%2C%20and%20has%20been%20reduced%20to%20a%20shell%20of%20its%20former%20self.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20investigation%20by%20the%20London%20School%20of%20Hygiene%20and%20Tropical%20Medicine%20found%20that%2026%2C000%20people%20were%20killed%20in%20the%20capital%20alone%20between%20April%202023%20and%20June%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEntire%20neighbourhoods%20have%20been%20taken%20over%20by%20fighters%20while%20at%20least%203.6%20million%20civilians%20have%20fled%2C%20according%20to%20the%20United%20Nations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThose%20unable%20or%20unwilling%20to%20leave%20have%20reported%20frequent%20artillery%20fire%20on%20residential%20areas%2C%20and%20widespread%20hunger%20in%20besieged%20neighbourhoods%20blockaded%20by%20opposing%20forces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20least%20106%2C000%20people%20are%20estimated%20to%20be%20suffering%20from%20famine%20in%20Khartoum%2C%20according%20to%20the%20UN-backed%20Integrated%20Food%20Security%20Phase%20Classification%2C%20with%20a%20further%203.2%20million%20experiencing%20crisis%20levels%20of%20hunger.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENationwide%2C%20famine%20has%20been%20declared%20in%20five%20areas%20--%20most%20of%20them%20in%20Darfur%20--%20and%20is%20expected%20to%20take%20hold%20of%20five%20more%20by%20May.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20auto-generated%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738462080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2Fskovb7c8_sudan-civil-war_625x300_02_February_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2F56-killed-158-injured-in-busy-sudan-market-as-civil-war-intensifies-7614473%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Artillery%20shelling%20and%20air%20strikes%20killed%20at%20least%2056%20people%20across%20greater%20Khartoum%2C%20according%20to%20a%20medical%20source%20and%20activists%2C%20the%20latest%20bloodshed%20in%20Sudan's%20devastating%20war.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2F56-killed-158-injured-in-busy-sudan-market-as-civil-war-intensifies-7614473%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'A%20political%20selection%3B%20a%20joke'%3A%20Ex-cricketers%20slam%20Pakistan's%20CT%20squad%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738461846000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-117847878%2Cimgsize-66312.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Ficc-champions-trophy-2025%2Fa-political-selection-a-joke-former-cricketers-slam-pakistans-champions-trophy-squad%2Farticleshow%2F117847823.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Former%20Pakistan%20captain%20Rashid%20Latif%20criticises%20the%20squad%20for%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%202025%20as%20a%20'political%20selection%2C'%20questioning%20the%20inclusion%20of%