ider.com%2Fsober-celebrities-who-dont-drink-do-drugs%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eactive%20alcoholic%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%20could%20hardly%20take%20care%20of%20herself%20%E2%80%94%20let%20alone%20her%20children.%20When%20I%20finally%20did%20get%20sober%20and%20didn't%20really%20know%20how%20to%20live%20without%20alcohol%2C%20Molly%20taught%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20doesn't%20know%20it%20and%20maybe%20she%20wasn't%20trying%20to%2C%20but%20she%20made%20the%20things%20that%20felt%20so%20hard%20to%20me%20look%20so%20easy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20her%20parents%20split%20and%20life%20changed%20from%20one%20house%20to%20two%2C%20she%20became%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcoparenting-community-parents-only-children-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esecond%20parent%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20her%20siblings%20in%20both%20homes%3B%20she%20simply%20stepped%20up.%20Too%20much%20has%20fallen%20on%20her%20shoulders%2C%20yet%20she%20never%20wavers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20is%20calm%20in%20the%20chaos%20%E2%80%94%20always.%20She%20is%20loving%20and%20patient%20%E2%80%94%20always.%20She%20is%20a%20leader%20%E2%80%94%20our%20leader%20%E2%80%94%20and%20we%20lean%20on%20her%20(even%20though%20we%20shouldn't).%20Molly%20has%20always%20made%20everything%20look%20easy%20despite%20the%20fact%20that%20nothing%20in%20her%20life%20has%20ever%20truly%20been%20that.%20For%20as%20long%20as%20I%20can%20remember%2C%20I%20have%20looked%20up%20to%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d1d15bc7-f8c1-464f-bff5-474515382c78%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ENow%20she's%20taking%20steps%20I%20am%20too%20afraid%20to%20take%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20want%20your%20advice.%26quot%3B%20She%20said%20it%20with%20a%20smile%2C%20a%20pep%2C%20and%20well-deserved%20pride.%20She%20didn't%20say%20it%20rudely.%20I%20didn't%20feel%20rejected%20or%20less%20than%2C%20but%20I%20did%20feel%20jealous.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20wasn't%20the%20first%20time%20I%20wished%20I