l%20Examiner's%20office.%20The%20cause%20of%20death%20remains%20unknown%2C%20but%20it%20has%20led%20to%20some%20criticisms%20online%20over%20the%20sometimes%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwall-street-transfixed-by-bofa-banker-leo-lukenas-untimely-death-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egrueling%20demands%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20can%20be%20placed%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwall-street-rising-stars-full-list%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eyoung%20Wall%20Street%20professionals%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHandler%20on%20Saturday%20blasted%20what%20he%20called%20%26quot%3Bunfounded%2C%20vitriolic%20attacks.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20this%20point%2C%20nobody%20knows%20exactly%20what%20happened%20and%20engaging%20in%20speculation%20with%20cynical%20assumptions%20serves%20no%20useful%20purpose%20and%20only%20adds%20to%20the%20grief%20that%20the%20McIntosh%20family%20is%20suffering%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDallas%20police%20said%20they%20are%20investigating%20McIntosh's%20passing.%20%26quot%3BBased%20on%20the%20date%2C%20approximate%20time%2C%20and%20location%2C%20this%20incident%20is%20being%20investigated%20as%20an%20unexplained%20death%2C%26quot%3B%20Michael%20Dennis%2C%20a%20public%20information%20officer%20for%20the%20Dallas%20police%2C%20told%20BI%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHandler%20said%20he%20spent%20time%20with%20junior%20members%20of%20the%20Dallas%20office%20on%20Thursday%20and%20offered%20support%20for%20anyone%20grieving%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foverworked-years-until-child-realized-work-doesnt-care-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eoverworked%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%2C%20whether%20it%20is%20being%20overwhelmed%20by%20the%20sadness%20of%20Carter%E2%80%99s%20passing%20or%20getting%20overloaded%20by%20work%20or%20even%20feeling%20like%20there%20are%20things%20in%20your%20personal%20life%20that%20seem%20unmanageable%2C%20always%20feel%20free%20to%20reach%20out%20to%20us%20or%20to%20any%20of%20our%20highly%20capable%20senior%20leaders%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20spokesman%20for%20Jefferies%20declined%20to%20comment.%20%3Cspan%3EBloomberg%20earlier%20reported%20on%20the%20memo.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20a%20copy%20of%20the%20memo%20Handler%20sent%20to%20staff%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Caside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Thursday%2C%20I%20spent%20time%20with%20the%20junior%20members%20of%20our%20Dallas%20office%20to%20listen%20and%20understand%20what%20they%20are%20feeling.%20%C2%A0I%20also%20wanted%20to%20personally%20express%20my%20heartfelt%20condolences%20on%20the%20terribly%20sad%20passing%20of%20Carter%20McIntosh%20and%20to%20make%20sure%20they%20(and%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20firm)%20know%20that%20both%20Brian%20and%20I%2C%20and%20every%20leader%20at%20Jefferies%2C%20are%20here%20at%20any%20time%20if%20anyone%20needs%20support%20or%20help.%C2%A0%20I%20was%20touched%20by%20what%20I%20heard%20about%20Carter%20being%20such%20a%20warm%2C%20outgoing%20colleague%20who%20had%20a%20joy%20for%20life%20and%20was%20so%20welcoming%20to%20everyone.%20%C2%A0It%20is%20clear%20what%20a%20well-liked%20and%20respected%20professional%20Carter%20was%20and%20how%20his%20loss%20has%20deeply%20impacted%20the%20office%20and%2C%20as%20I%20have%20heard%20from%20many%20outside%20Dallas%2C%20all%20of%20Jefferies.%20%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20hope%20that%20all%20of%20you%20who%20know%20me%20understand%20how%20personally%20heartbreaking%20this%20is%20for%20me.%20%C2%A0I%20think%20you%20know%20that%20I%20spend%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20with%20our%20analysts%20and%20associates%2C%20not%20out%20of%20obligation%20but%20because%20I%20truly%20respect%20them%20and%20get%20more%20pleasure%20out%20of%20the%20experience%20than%20I%20can%20possibly%20offer%20in%20return.%20%C2%A0I%20do%20my%20best%20to%20share%20my%20perspectives%20with%2