e%20users.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ESingle%20adults%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-dating-apps-changing-new-startups-take-on-tinder-hinge%23%3A~%3Atext%3DDating%2520apps%2520are%2520in%2520for%2Cas%2520incumbents%2520lose%2520their%2520luster.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efed%20up%20with%20dating%20apps%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Emight%20be%20turning%20to%20old-fashioned%20social%20media%20to%20find%20their%20next%20partner%20instead.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstagram%20is%20the%20most%20popular%20place%20to%20meet%20and%20communicate%20with%20a%20potential%20partner%2C%20at%20least%20for%20the%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%20of%20people%20using%20Rizz%2C%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frizz-dating-app-ai-analyzes-text-screenshot-conversations-advice-2024-6%23%3A~%3Atext%3DRizz%2520is%2520an%2520AI%252Dpowered%2C%252C%2520responses%252C%2520and%2520decodes%2520screenshots.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAI%20dating%20assistant%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finternet-slang-tiktok-word-rizz-rizzler-rizzgod-zoomers-rizzardofoz-twitter-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERizz%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20is%20slang%20for%20charisma%2C%20launched%20in%202022.%20It%20functions%20like%20a%20dating%20coach%2C%20helping%20users%20craft%20witty%20responses%20to%20messages%20and%20less%20cringey%20pick-up%20lines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDating%20coaches%20charge%20%2430%20to%20%24300%20an%20hour.%20Not%20everybody%20can%20afford%20paying%20over%20%2430%20an%20hour.%20So%20the%20moment%20ChatGPT%20launched%2C%20I%20already%20had%20this%20idea%20in%20the%20back%20of%20my%20mind%2C%26quot%3B%20Rizz%20cofounder%20and%20CEO%20Roman%20Khaves%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUsers%20upload%20screenshots%20of%20conversations%20from%20dating%20apps%2C%20messaging%20apps%2C%20or%20social%20media%20to%20Rizz%2C%20which%20then%20generates%20a%20response.%20The%20app%20leverages%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feverything-you-need-to-know-about-chat-gpt-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChatGPT%3C%2Fa%3E%20but%20fine-tunes%20its%20responses%20based%20on%20prior%20responses%20it%20generated.%20So%20the%20more%20you%20use%20it%2C%20the%20better%20and%20more%20personalized%20its%20responses%20will%20be%2C%20Khaves%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERizz%20costs%20%247%20a%20week%20or%20%2420%20a%20month%20and%20has%20about%20half%20a%20million%20monthly%20active%20users.%20The%20platform's%20user%20base%20is%2065%25%20male%20and%2035%25%20female%20and%20most%20of%20them%20fall%20between%2018%20and%2035.%20They're%20largely%20from%20English-speaking%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKhaves%20shared%20data%20with%20BI%20showing%20that%2022%25%20of%20the%20screenshots%20uploaded%20to%20Rizz%20now%20come%20from%20Instagram%2C%20an%208%25%20increase%20from%20a%20year%20ago.%20About%2015%25%20come%20from%20iMessage%20and%2011%25%20from%20WhatsApp.%20Dating%20apps%20comprise%20a%20smaller%20share%2C%20with%20Tinder%20at%2011%25%2C%20Hinge%20at%2010%25%2C%20and%20Bumble%20at%204%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22767%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Rizz%20screenshot%20data%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F679e3d64eb4be2fff9a3307e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22575%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMessaging%20and%20social%20media%20are%20a%20growing%20destination%20for%20dating%2C%20according%20to%20data%20from%20Rizz.%3Cp%3ERizz%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20uncommon%20for%20potential%20partners%20to%20meet%20on%20a%20dating%20app%20and%20quickly%20move%20their%20conversation%20to%20text%20or%20even%20Instagram.%20But%20Rizz%20sees%20evidence%20in%20the%20data%20that%20Instagram%20is%20becoming%20a%20first-choice%20destination%20for%20dating.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BInstagram%20has%20evolved%20into%20this%20fascinating%20dual-purpose%20platform%20for%20relationships%2C%26quot%3B%20Khaves%20said.%20%26quot%3BWhether%20it's%20sliding%20into%20DMs%20or%20naturally%20connecting%20through%20shared%20content%2C%20people%20are%20both%20starting%20and%20deepening%20their%20connections%20entirely%20within%20Instagram.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDating%20on%20Instagram%20isn't%20new.%20Celebrity%20couples%20%E2%80%94%20like%20Joe%20Jonas%20and%20Sophie%20Turner%2C%20or%20exes%20Dua%20Lipa%20and%20Anwar%20Hadid%20%E2%80%94%20and%20regular%20couples%20alike%20have%20found%20love%20on%20Instagram.%20The%20data%20from%20Rizz%20shows%20it's%20only%20becoming%20more%20popular%20as%20users%20give%20up%20on%20regular%20dating%20apps.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERizz's%20algorithms%20can%20track%20the%20source%20of%20screenshots%2C%20distinguishing%20whether%20a%20user%20uploads%20them%20from%20an%20Instagram%20story%20or%20a%20direct%20message.%20What's%20less%20clear%20is%20the%20history%20behind%20the%20relationship.%20%26quot%3BThe%20one%20thing%20we%20don't%20know%20is%20how%20long%20they%20know%20the%20person%2C%20whether%20they've%20been%20friends%20with%20them%20on%20Instagram%20for%20a%20while%20or%20not%2C%26quot%3B%20Khaves%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERizz%20is%20already%20developing%20features%20tailored%20to%20Instagram%2C%20where%20the%20first%20move%20could%20be%20linked%20to%20a%20story%20or%20a%20picture%20rather%20than%20a%20prompt%20on%20Hinge.%20Instagram%20also%20introduced%20a%20feature%20in%20September%20that%20allows%20users%20to%20leave%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-instagram-launched-stories-comments-users-creators-chat-feature-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecomments%20under%20stories%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20making%20it%20easier%20for%20mutual%20followers%20to%20interact%20with%20each%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20reason%20people%20are%20moving%20away%20from%20dating%20apps%20might%20be%20simple