%20fascinating%20tension%20between%20two%20competing%20visions.%20One%20focuses%20on%20pursuing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-is-agi-artificial-general-intelligence-explained-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eartificial%20general%20intelligence%3C%2Fa%3E%20(AGI)%20through%20increasingly%20powerful%20and%20comprehensive%20models.%20The%20other%20emphasizes%20practical%20applications%20through%20efficient%20models%20and%20methods%20targeted%20at%20specific%20use%20cases%20and%20benchmarks%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20comparing%20OpenAI%20and%20DeepSeek.%20%26quot%3BThis%20tension%20drives%20innovation%20in%20both%20directions%2C%20and%20also%20exists%20within%20the%20big%20companies.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPukar%20Hamal%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsecuritypal-raise-venture-capital-funding-without-pitch-deck-a16z-2022-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESecurityPal%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20helps%20companies%20like%20OpenAI%20complete%20security%20questionnaires%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Esaid%20the%20industry%20should%20temper%20expectations%20of%20immediate%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20the%20DeepSeek%20team%20truly%20can%20cut%20training%20and%20inference%20costs%20by%20an%20order%20of%20magnitude%2C%20it%20could%20spark%20far%20broader%20deployment%20of%20AI%20than%20analysts%20anticipate%2C%26quot%3B%20Hamal%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BOn%20the%20flip%20side%2C%20it'll%20take%20more%20than%20a%20few%20tough%20earnings%20calls%20to%20make%20the%20biggest%20AI%20players%20reconsider%20the%20staggering%20GPU%20investments%20we're%20seeing%20for%202025.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmark-zuckerberg-meta-ai-investment-capital-expenditure-datacenter-deepseek-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMeta%20recently%20committed%20%2460%20billion%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20AI%20infrastructure%20investments.%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20also%20announced%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-ai-stargate-openai-oracle-softbank-technology-investment-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EStargate%3C%2Fa%3E%20last%20month%2C%20a%20joint%20venture%20between%20OpenAI%2C%20Oracle%2C%20and%20SoftBank%20that%20will%20invest%20%24500%20billion%20into%20AI%20infrastructure%20across%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20biggest%20debates%20among%20AI%20innovators%20is%20whether%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-ai-yann-lecun-deepseek-open-source-openai-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eopen-source%20models%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20the%20public%20can%20access%20and%20modify%2C%20are%20more%20likely%20to%20drive%20breakthroughs%20than%20closed-source%20models.%20OpenAI%20says%20it%20keeps%20its%20models%20closed%20for%20safety%2C%20while%20DeepSeek's%20models%20are%20open-source.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESatya%20Nitta%2C%20the%20cofounder%20and%20CEO%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.emergence.ai%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEmergence%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20company%20developing%20AI%20agents%2C%20said%20that%20%26quot%3BDeepSeek%20R1%20is%20a%20meaningful%20advance%20in%20broadening%20access%20to%20AI%20reasoning%2C%20spotlighting%20the%20power%20of%20open%20source%20and%20setting%20a%20new%20benchmark%20for%20reasoning.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHamal%20said%20we%20should%20still%20approach%20open-source%20development%20cautiously%20%E2%80%94%20even%20if%20it'll%20eventually%20dominate%20the%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAn%20'open%20source'%20model%20of%20unknown%20alignment%20invites%20serious%20public%20safety%20and%20regulatory%20questions.%20If%20DeepSeek's%20mobile%20app%20keeps%20climbing%20the%20charts%2C%20we%20could%20end%20up%20with%20a%20discussion%20similar%20to%20the%20recent%20calls%20to%20block%20TikTok%20in%20the%20US%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20White%20House%20advisor%20David%20Sacks%20also%20raised%20concerns%20about%20DeepSeek's%20training%20methods%20when%20he%20told%20Fox%20News%20that%20it%20is%20'possible'%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdeepseek-openai-data-training-distillation-david-sacks-microsoft-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDeepSeek%20used%20OpenAI's%20models%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20train%20its%20own%20AI%20model.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20%26quot%3Bopenness%20typically%20wins%20in%20the%20long%20run%2C%26quot%3B%20Hamal%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20DeepSeek%20helps%20reset%20an%20increasingly%20closed%20foundational%20model%20market%2C%20that%20can%20be%20a%20net%20positive%20%E2%80%94%20so%20long%20as%20we%20maintain%20the%20guardrails%20that%20protect%20customers%20and%20the%20public%20at%20large.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20there's%20one%20lesson%20AI%20executives%20are%20taking%20away%20from%20this%20week%2C%20though%2C%20it's%20that%20it's%20possible%20to%20do%20more%20with%20fewer%20resources.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMatthew%20Putman%2C%20CEO%20of%20Nanotronics%2C%20which%20designs%20AI-controlled%20factories%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BTo%20me%2C%20the%20competition%20itself%20is%20less%20significant%20than%20the%20validation%20of%20a%20broader%20principle%3A%20AI%20models%20can%20be%20built%20more%20affordably%20and%20applied%20far%20beyond%20large%20language%20models.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdeepseek-ai-startups-us-opportunity-open-source-low-cost-training-2025-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738420309000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F679cd07deb4be2fff9a30d5c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdeepseek-ai-startups-us-opportunity-open-source-low-cost-training-2025-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22DeepSeek's%20success%20creates%20better%20chanc